# KILL_SWITCH
# 
# Create this file to emergency-stop all trading.
# 
# When /opt/hermes-trader/KILL_SWITCH exists:
#   - No new orders (paper or live)
#   - Position monitoring continues
#   - Exit management allowed only to reduce risk
#   - Telegram reports indicate KILL SWITCH ACTIVE
#
# To activate:  touch /opt/hermes-trader/KILL_SWITCH
# To deactivate: rm /opt/hermes-trader/KILL_SWITCH (user only, not agent)
#
# The agent will never create or remove this file.
# Only the user may manage it.